missionaries_and_cannibals.zip
  -- java:
  		-- src: the source folder
  		-- missionaries_and_cannibals.jar: the executable binaries
  -- prolog:
  		-- missionaries_and_cannibals.pl
  -- python:
  		-- missionaries_and_cannibals.py
  -- report:
  		-- report.pdf: the report with the comparison of the solutions


To run the Java version:
-------------------------
> java -jar missionaries_and_cannibals.jar


To run the Prolog code in SWI-Prolog:
-------------------------------------
?- ['missionaries_and_cannibals.pl'].
?- find.


To run the Python version:
--------------------------
> python missionaries_and_cannibals.py
